+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01XYLJiWynXYK4fBNfCYh6Qx","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good. Now let me make the design decisions quickly and write the design document, then move to TDD implementation.\n\n**Design decisions (autopilot):**\n\n1. **Architecture**: Single-module approach with a few well-separated concerns: cell parsing, formula evaluation, dependency graph, and the Spreadsheet facade. All in `src/`.\n\n2. **Formula Parsing**: Recursive descent parser — simple, no dependencies, handles operator precedence correctly.\n\n3. **Dependency Tracking**: Adjacency list graph with topological sort for recalculation order. Detect cycles via DFS during dependency resolution.\n\n4. **Reactive Updates**: On `set()`, parse the value, update the dependency graph, detect cycles, then topologically sort dependents and recompute in order.\n\n5. **Cell Reference Parsing**: Regex-based extraction of cell refs (e.g., `A1`, `AA99`) and ranges (e.g., `A1:C3`).\n\n6. **File Structure**:\n   - `src/index.ts` — Spreadsheet class (public API)\n   - `src/parser.ts` — Formula tokenizer and recursive descent parser\n   - `src/types.ts` — Shared types (AST nodes, cell value types)\n   - `src/utils.ts` — Cell reference utilities (parsing, column conversion, range expansion)\n\nLet me write the design doc and then move to TDD."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":933,"cache_read_input_tokens":23013,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":933},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b246dfe4-021c-4239-9ce1-7fa9c34fdd5c","uuid":"48b56700-f602-43cd-a7d3-4e1a85104313"}
